title: 02/02/2021 - HOUR 2 - Top 10 Players in the Super Bowl, Peter King, Eric Dickerson
itunes:title: 02/02/2021 - HOUR 2 - Top 10 Players in the Super Bowl, Peter King, Eric Dickerson
description:
In this hour of The Herd with Colin Cowherd, we get Colin's top 10 players in the Super Bowl. Also, Peter King of nbcsports.com on the blockbuster Jared Goff-Matthew Stafford swap. Finally, Hall of Fame running back Eric Dickerson on how Stafford fits in the Los Angeles Rams' system.
